data.name: HowToUseMainText.Text
data.value:
Hosting :
Playing online: Send your friends your public ip. (You can find it in the top left.) Make sure you have 27015 port forwarded with UDP and TCP Then finally click START to run the mod
Playing locally (Or with hamachi.): Send your friends the local ip and click START
Joining: Step 1: Open the console in game (Details in video or online.) Step 2: Type "connect HOSTIP" (Replace HOSTIP obviously) Step 3:Press [ENTER] to connect!
